        "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nHi Jim,\n\nThe cost of the method is we could not call Java API freely in JavaScript.\n\nIn my testing, with below script\nhttps://github.com/mozilla/rhino/blob/master/examples/liveConnect.js\nIt throws exception like this:\nTypeError: Cannot find function append in object\n\nAnother option I have investigated was to customize JSON.stringify, so that it may be possible to integrate jackson to do the conversion. But Seems Rhino does not support this.",
